data.description: Don't miss out on this charming country home nestled on 6+ acres! Featuring a spacious living room with a cozy wood stove, a kitchen with an eating bar, & dining area. With the primary bedroom on the main floor, plus 2 additional bedrooms & a bonus room, there's ample space for everyone. Updates include new vinyl plank laminate flooring & fresh interior paint. Step outside to enjoy the covered patio & take in the serene surroundings. The property boasts a large 3-bay shop with 220 power, perfect for storage or projects, along with a 4000+ sq. ft older barn, ideal for animals or hobbies. Conveniently located minutes from shopping & I-5 access, & centrally positioned between Seattle & Portland, this country retreat awaits its new owner.
